name: Gourmet Chocolate Covered Pretzel Rods
description:
Pretzel Twists dipped in milk chocolate and sprinkled with any color sanding sugar you desire.

These also make great baby shower and wedding favors, so please ask about the other colors we can do and different packaging/quantities.

We do everything we can to keep them from breaking, but some breakage could occur.

The pretzels are all sent beautifully packaged in food safe cellophane bags tied with a ribbon. 

We will include a short handwritten note card for no extra charge. 

We can also try to use a certain ribbon color if you prefer, or we can do any holiday theme.
